{"tid":303400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖無碼】雜交換禮物","createTime":"2017-06-30T07:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T07:12:53.000Z","uid":6728,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8d4d4d685f818af8f2b771771a7d234a01372e","tid":303400,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"2015年10月21日 星期三 15:21<br />\n交換禮物 習近平贈女王彭麗媛唱片<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平倫敦當地時間20日，在英女王伊利沙白二世陪同下，到白金漢宮參觀王室中國藏品。而早前在私人午宴期間，習近平與英女王交換禮物，當中包括夫人彭麗媛的音樂專輯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/realtimenews/article_image/can20151021/250F1D571805221636233A2A9F1672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle_image%2Fcan20151021%2F250F1D571805221636233A2A9F1672.jpg&h=def865d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb83e92390f341003a8fd415aa624c4ee07600d3","tid":303400,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}